-- Ashok Leyland to Acquire 26% of U.K.'s Bus Maker Optare For $7.5 Million
-- Tuhin Kar
-- 2010-07-29T10:16:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-29/ashok-leyland-to-acquire-26-of-u-k-s-bus-maker-optare-for-7-5-million.html

          
          
             Ashok Leyland Ltd. to acquire 26
percent stake in U.K.-based maker of single and double-deck
buses Optare Plc for about $7.5 million, according to a
statement today on the National Stock Exchange.  
          
          


  


        